{"tid":2310511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★小米超 Apple 成第三 Samsung仍居第一","createTime":"2020-12-03T10:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T10:14:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68208b974510eb15472b6da0170ae0a80bcbc199","tid":2310511,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"據資訊科技研究和顧問公司 Gartner 周一（30 日）發表的調查報告，智能電話在第三季共在全球賣出 3.66 億部，比起去年同期減 5.7%，其估計是受疫情影響，消費者正面對經濟不確定性和對下一波爆發的擔憂，故對購買非必需品的意欲減少。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n不過，南韓 Samsung 以及中國小米的銷售表現則是有增無減。數據顯示，Samsung 銷量保持第一，在第三季度共賣出 8080 萬部電話，比起去年同期成長 2.2%，而小米更是爆增 35%，共賣4440 萬部。<br />\n<br />\n而有 iPhone 12 熱潮加持的 Apple，在第三季度銷量仍小跌 0.6%，賣出 4060 萬部電話，數量只是 Samsung 的一半左右，亦被中國小米超越，被擠到第四名，Gartner 估計主要原因是其推遲了其新一代 iPhone 的發貨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/03/global-smartphone-sales/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F03%2Fglobal-smartphone-sales%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=736de7f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/03/global-smartphone-sales/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"e4dc4b348b9bf0750c4d173765bfd102cbe524e8","tid":2310511,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"支cook go to hell<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30ce3c78246245f5dac642263c0499f86db65f8","tid":2310511,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:09:59.000Z","msg":"用緊iPhone 都買咗2部A71俾兩老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaeacf5b9508c491ec064c5dd2b572ef6d9adc85","tid":2310511,"uid":246691,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"